Either the V1P0 or V2P5 rail has failed to come up. V1P0 is first in the sequence, its PG is the EN for V2P5.

Software control for the FPGA1_TO_PHY_COMA_MODE net. Only effective after PHY initialization.
Setting this bit to 1 will clear the timed out state of the V1P0 and V2P5 rail controllers, allowing PHY power sequencing to be attempted again.
